window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Widow Bella is pregnant, destitute, and in debt. Her only way out is marriage to a stranger.</b></p> <p>As she travels to Arizona, Bella hopes for a better life. The rancher she is to marry needs someone to care for his three children. Bella knows this will only be a marriage of convenience and is grateful for a new start.</p> <p>Shane's ranch is what has kept him going since his wife passed four years ago. He tends to his children as best he can, vowing never to marry again. When Bella arrives, Shane's life unravels and is turned upside down. Not wanting her there, Shane plans to send her back home. But Bella has no home to go back to, and Shane has a secret about to tear his family, and Bella's life, apart.</p>"; 
